We have logged $numbertool.number($numConf) conferences and $numbertool.number($numPres) presentations into the system since 2008.

The table below lists all the conferences we know about; if you don't see a conference you plan to present a talk or poster at, you can add it by entering its name in the blue box below and clicking "$escapetool.xml($services.localization.render('event.createEvent.create'))".

A number of dynamic pages are available to help you navigate the conferences and presentations in the system, including a list of all upcoming conferences, a list of all your presentations, and, for members of SAPO, a list of presentations you are reviewing. For more infomation see the dynamic reports page.
